# Resume Parser Accuracy Test Report

> **Date:** March 2, 2026  
> **Dataset:** 120 IT resumes from `INFORMATION-TECHNOLOGY/` directory  
> **Processing Time:** ~4 minutes (avg 2,035ms/resume)

---

## Overall Results

| Metric | Value | Grade |
|--------|-------|-------|
| **Overall Quality Score** | **29.9%** | **F** |
| Parse Success Rate | 100% | All PDFs parsed |
| Overall Extraction Rate | 27.2% | Very Low |

> [!CAUTION]
> The parser is performing very poorly on this dataset. The primary issues are in **entity extraction** (name, email, phone) and **experience extraction**, NOT in skills extraction.

